text: Agung Setyabudi (born 2 November 1972 in Solo, Central Java) is an Indonesian footballer, he normally plays as a defender and is tall. He is former player for the Indonesia national football team, playing in the Olympic Games qualifiers, Tiger Cup and Asian Cup.
